gov.nasa.worldwind.animation

Class AngleAnimator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.worldwind.animation.BasicAnimator
      • gov.nasa.worldwind.animation.AngleAnimator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Animator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RotateToAngleAnimator

    public class AngleAnimator
extends BasicAnimator
    Animates angles, via an interpolator. begin and end values can be reset once the animation is already in motion.
